version_description:
Exclusive Live Blogs added to Match Centres. 
FOX SPORTS TV shows added to sport sections.
We’ve also added The Crowd so you can access all the content posted on our community.  
Plus, we’ve squashed a few bugs.
As always, your feedback is encouraged, we want to hear from you, to help make the app better everyday for you.
